der electric conductivity is proportional to the\nn-1-th derivative of the n-th order thermal conductivity for the nonlinear WF\nlaw.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 20 Apr 2022 01:43:15 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-08-17"}
